{"lastModified":1772613566763,"uri":"c::15406789740::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Preveza and Athens, Greece\n\nWe are proud to welcome the brand-new Aquila 54 to our fleet – a next-generation power catamaran designed for luxurious, long-range cruising with the space, comfort, and performance Aquila is renowned for. Built for private and charter guests alike, this 54-foot masterpiece offers expansive outdoor living areas, a fully equipped flybridge, and a beautifully appointed interior with multiple layout options.\n\nPerfect for exploring the Greek islands in ultimate comfort, the Aquila 54 will be available for charter starting 2026, delivering a premium yachting experience for families and groups seeking space, stability, and seamless service onboard. Whether anchored in a quiet bay or underway between island destinations, guests will enjoy a smooth and spacious ride with panoramic views, gourmet meals, and personalized attention from a dedicated crew.","blueprint":{"name":"MARY'S GRACE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c01ca6c0-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c0249600-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c01ccdd0-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c01839f0-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c0172880-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c0255950-01a9-11f1-9c77-67f7662804eb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1fef2ad0-01a7-11f1-9813-c983860a136e::assets::c01d1bf0-01a9-11f1-9c77-6